# .bobignore — Boréal project
# Restricts Bob from reading sensitive or irrelevant files.
# Syntax: same as .gitignore

# === Secrets & credentials ===
.env
.env.*
*.key
*.pem
secrets/
config/credentials.json
config/secrets.json

# === Personally Identifiable Information (PII) ===
# Insurance policy data may contain customer names, addresses,
# policy numbers, license plates, VINs. Bob must not read these.
demo/sample-policies/raw/
demo/sample-policies/*.original.pdf
demo/boreal-test-policy.pdf
demo/customer-data/
**/*pii*
**/*personal*

# === System & build artifacts ===
node_modules/
dist/
build/
.cache/
.tmp/
*.log

# === IDE & OS ===
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# === Notes ===
# When working with real or sample policy PDFs, place sanitized
# (redacted) copies in demo/sample-policies/ for Bob to read.
# Originals (if any) go in demo/sample-policies/raw/ — gitignored.

# Made with Bob
